A platform to help nurture Kenya's ever growing fashion industry was created at Brew Bistro and lounge to help upcoming and established designers showcase their work.The show, hosted on Friday of every week, is characterised by a selected designer showcasing and selling his or her creativity to revellers.Designers featured included Koki Designs by Kokeeb Zameed Pinard, who showcased her ladies' and gentlemen's wears modified with a cultural touch.The platform also features models and make-up artistes.